          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> Bard grown desirous of saving his pelf,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-2" n="2">Built a house he was sure would hold none but himself:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-3" n="3">This enrag'd god <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi>, who <hi rend="italics">Mercury</hi> sent,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-4" n="4">And bid him go ask what his votary meant.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-5" n="5">Some foe to my empire has been his adviser,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-6" n="6">'Tis of dreadful portent when a poet turns miser:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-7" n="7">Tell him, <hi rend="italics">Hermes</hi>, from me, tell that subject of mine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-8" n="8">I have sworn, by the <hi rend="italics">Styx</hi>, to defeat his design;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-9" n="9">For where-ever he comes the muses shall reign;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C27A1-line-10" n="10">And the muses, he knows, have a numerous train.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
